org.csstudio.platform.model
Class CentralItemFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.csstudio.platform.model.CentralItemFactory

public final class CentralItemFactory
extends java.lang.Object

A factory for control system items. Central control system items (e.g. IProcessVariables), can be obtained by static creation methods.

Author:
Sven Wende
